          <text>in <cato:entity-ref xmlns:cato="http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml" entity-type="act" value="Higher Education Act of 1965/s:428/ss:b/p:1/sp:M/cl:i">clause (i)</cato:entity-ref>, by
