          <enum>(6)</enum>
          <text>by inserting
			 after <cato:entity-ref xmlns:cato="http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml" entity-type="act" value="Higher Education Act of 1965/s:428/ss:b/p:1/sp:M/cl:iii">clause (iii)</cato:entity-ref> the following:</text>
