              <text>in the case of
				any borrower who has received a call or order to duty described in <cato:entity-ref xmlns:cato="http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml" entity-type="act" value="Higher Education Act of 1965/s:428/ss:b/p:1/sp:M/cl:iii/scl:I">subclause
