							<subclause id="id5BA0E392D7714BB19E1F3C9442D15319">
                <enum>(I)</enum>
                <text>in the case of
				any borrower described in such clause whose call or order to duty is cancelled
				before the first day of the service described in <cato:entity-ref xmlns:cato="http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml" entity-type="act" value="Higher Education Act of 1965/s:428/ss:b/p:1/sp:M/cl:iii/scl:I">subclause (I)</cato:entity-ref> or <cato:entity-ref xmlns:cato="http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml" entity-type="act" value="Higher Education Act of 1965/s:428/ss:b/p:1/sp:M/cl:iii/scl:II">(II) of
				clause (iii)</cato:entity-ref> because of a personal injury in connection with training to
				prepare for such service, during the period described in <cato:entity-ref xmlns:cato="http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml" entity-type="act" value="Higher Education Act of 1965/s:428/ss:b/p:1/sp:M/cl:iv" proposed="true">clause (iv)</cato:entity-ref> and during
